formating css is there because you can change the font size and change it to dark mode and light mode
to use this
if you are making a new css, add @import './Formatting.css';
then to use the variables in the formatting, add var(--bg-color)
example:
background-color: var(--bg-color);


you can also change the values of these attribute in Formatting css
if you don't like the color